# Stage 2 → 3 Wireframe Skeleton IR Placeholder

This file documents the expected Stage 3 artifact locations for the stage-2-to-3
handoff bundle. Phase 3 Plan 01 (03-01) ships the real Excalidraw emitter.

## Artifact locations (per sketch.md workflow)

The sketch workflow emits artifacts to:

```
.design-os/preview/<run-id>/wireframes/<screen>/skeleton-ir.json
.design-os/preview/<run-id>/wireframes/<screen>/v1.excalidraw
.design-os/preview/<run-id>/wireframes/<screen>/v2.excalidraw
...
.design-os/preview/<run-id>/wireframes/<screen>/v8.excalidraw
.design-os/preview/<run-id>/wireframes/<screen>/CHOICE.md
```

## Screens from Stage 2 sitemap

Screens to wireframe (from `upstream/sitemap.json` v1-category variant):

- `search-results` — primary JTBD: "Surface relevant context when starting a task"
- `workspace-overview` — primary JTBD: "Manage active work in context"

## Wireframe naming convention (OQ-4 resolution)

Variants are named `v1.excalidraw` through `v8.excalidraw` (numeric, sortable).

